item.title: [PI] Staff Zone
item.dc:creator: @mr_extremez mr extremez
item.description:
@mr_extremez wrote:

to add bank booths open up your source and go to src/server/world/objectmanager.java then add this and replace the bolded words with the bank booth info
c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(OBJECT_ID, X_COORDINATE, Y_COORDINATE, FACE_ORIENTATION, OBJECT_TYPE);
